{"type":"answer","id":146564,"parentType":"question","parentId":16941,"uid":21384,"contents":"怎么说呢，我不敢肯定&quot;天意&quot;的不存在。<br>\n<br>\n但坦白的说，有时候这么做，只是为了捉住民众的心而已，支持这种想法的越多，反对派达成目的的几率就越高，通俗点说这就是历史赐予求变者的一次偶然的机会，有失败的，也有成功的，巨大的成功往往就会成为故事流传下来，还越传越神乎。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/k8w1dlo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/k8w1dlo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/k8w1dlo.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWGLvsS.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWGLvsS.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWGLvsS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-01","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}